        <div class="websiteFont__hero">
            We don't want you to miss our wedding. Here you will have the wedding ceremony and the wedding reception venues addresses in handy. No excuses for being late!
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<hr class="small_hr" />

<div class="row mt-5 justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-6 weddingvenueaddress ">
